{"tid":640261,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"婦撞警隱形戰車屈錢","createTime":"2018-04-24T07:09:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-24T11:54:42.000Z","uid":19287,"like":64,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"6f4b3f65a81d59a92d041f2880afc2155e24b183","tid":640261,"uid":19287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T07:09:44.000Z","msg":"【本報訊】扮被車撞「屈錢黨」婦人有眼不識泰山，竟強屈警方交通部一輛隱形戰車，無所遁形下涉企圖以欺騙手段取得財產被捕。被捕婦人69歲姓潘，昨晨10時許，她在牛頭角常悅道與偉業街交界橫過馬路時，懷疑故意撞向一輛駛至私家車，惟駕車司機及時煞停，她未有受傷及拒絕送院，但向司機索賠償。誰知私家車為隸屬東九龍交通部隱形戰車，警員盤查後，潘婦承認屈錢被捕"},{"pid":"aba11ff8ef3fdd08b2f34e51e1713719e05ee919","tid":640261,"uid":54930,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T07:11:02.000Z","msg":"世界大戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c96f706ba1c6ceefa0b848d4401787c54991087","tid":640261,"uid":118120,"like":2,"dislike":9,"score":-7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T07:11:06.000Z","msg":"香港都有扮撞車屈錢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f16bdb209a638adec43aa5fa7e64e63decc9b485","tid":640261,"uid":60831,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T07:11:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香港都有扮撞車屈錢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有咗好耐啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"553b309316e7cba98212790bc404f4adac342868","tid":640261,"uid":14103,"like":0,"dislike":12,"score":-12,"quote":{"pid":"f16bdb209a638adec43aa5fa7e64e63decc9b485","tid":640261,"uid":60831,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T07:11:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香港都有扮撞車屈錢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有咗好耐啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T07:12:47.000Z","msg":"以為大陸先有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c7578873f9a93371323f67073c1cf76dc27bb4