"e4e7cfe810a18d81e8aaf9eb2d2d962b9e56ee9a","tid":640261,"uid":33875,"like":4,"dislike":5,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T07:13:25.000Z","msg":"會唔會真係撞到人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T07:14:35.000Z","msg":"隱形戰車撞到人，屈佢屈錢拉佢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T07:15:40.000Z","msg":"都唔出奇喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T07:20:47.000Z","msg":"阿sir做野唔洗你教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d70a7e0179ba1ad2a1a5b82e30890ab41089863","tid":640261,"uid":116143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T07:21:55.000Z","msg":"正宗低撚死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52383383ea8e4c2ae5507bc8c3c514de3967ff82","tid":640261,"uid":38820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T07:23:10.000Z","msg":"回帶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56e44e4a64f81f6036f959d3f507c2df69835f1e","tid":640261,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"92bdc085910d4eefe4849e781c42d88a3c22228b","tid":640261,"uid":32832,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T07:15:03.000Z","msg":"撞車黨屈差佬錢被補<br />\n撞車黨屈市民錢俾車cam影低左報警，差佬唔理 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T07:25:05.000Z","msg":"果位巿民係咪可以告驚犬攞返賠償？"},{"pid":"c6c3859ac1b54745ac3ad0a0017c2f01a24d9440","tid":640261,"uid":61864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T07:25:57.000Z","msg":"回帶"},{"pid":"972bdbf22f9d08ba691b2f15b96db5985f6c81d6","tid":640261,"uid":65346,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T07:26:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180424/58111799\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180424%2F58111799&d=dwnxjq7AAAmXthCMTWeEyr%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=6bb6a46e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180424%2F58111799&h=5676652a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180424/58111799</a><br />\n<br />\n九龍塘又一村驚現碰瓷黨？！網上今日流傳一段車cam片段，片中可見在九龍塘達之路，一名中年婦拖著篋「走出」馬路，然後「加速」奔跑，撞向一部早已停下的私家車車頭，其間私家車接連「響號」也無法阻止中年婦的驚人行為。事件引起大量網民及駕駛者關注，擔心在國內頗流行的碰瓷黨騙案（騙徒以行人身份故意撞向汽車屈錢）已流入香港，不少留言者都敦促駕車一定要「裝車cam保平安」，也希望警方徹查涉案中年婦是否有詐騙的嫌疑。<br />\n<br />\n根據近日在fb流傳的13秒長車cam短片，顯示3月9日上午7時許，該輛私家車行沿九龍塘逹之路行駛，當時司機疑見到有中年婦拖著篋欲過馬路，故司機在該個有燈號的行人過路處前方逾五米早已收油及停車。<br />\n未料該名拖篋女子此時未有橫過馬路，反而帶著篋加速跑向私家車。私家車司機雖不斷響號，但仍無法阻止該女士，該女子最後側著身以膊頭猛撞向私家車車頭，「嘭」一聲後，她便連人帶篋「跌倒」地上消失於攝錄鏡頭上，片段至此結束。記者今日重返上述「車禍」現場，發現上址附近有不少店舖包括地產舖，但店員均指未有目擊事件。<br />\n不少網民均就事件留言，質疑是否有人故意製造「撞車」事故騙賠償，認為若是真的，警方應徹查甚至拘控，不少人都關注片中司機或車主有否被屈錢，也有人呼籲警方應考慮控告該中年婦「刑事毀壞」汽車。近年本港多次出現「碰瓷黨」疑雲，在港島區大坑道、沙田區也有司機在網上發佈「車Cam片」顯示有行人懷疑刻意被車撞到「搏賠償」，呼籲其他車主小心。"},{"pid":"b737ba8c23453c0f94f0283198a1a37935671f4b","tid":640261,"uid":83060,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T07:26:45.000Z","msg":"其實真係撞傷人，不過黑警屈返阿婆轉頭。"},{"pid":"f68e704d4572cf6c2351aeca7710e7d5abd087cb","tid":640261,"uid":48124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T11:37:34.000Z","msg":"隱形<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb65ff2e6549d1d4a44552ce74c106586e8affe3","tid":640261,"uid":34103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T11:40:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8c52e59c2a4658cf7045e27156ec74bebc9c7f61","tid":640261,"uid":74058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T11:40:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"466fa8fb41d1c0370ffe2e128202a67690609708","tid":640261,"uid":3068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T11:54:42.000Z","msg":"「碰瓷黨」<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">疑雲</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}